PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the MATHIAS COLOMB CREE NATION BAND surrenders, for a term of 25 years, several pieces of land (1.57 ha) on Pukatawaga Indian Reserve No. 198 in Manitoba, for the purpose of leasing them to third parties for residential, educational, institutional, commercial or industrial purposes.
